To be able to compile flcards for test, we need:

 get cards.devel
 cards.lib fltk fltk.devel \
 xorg-libx11 xorg-libx11.devel \
 xorg-libxext xorg-libxext.devel \
 xorg-libxfixes xorg-libxfixes.devel \
 xorg-libxft xorg-libxft.devel \
 xorg-libxrender xorg-libxrender.devel \
 xorg-libxinerama xorg-libxinerama.devel \
 mesa mesa.devel xorgproto

Then just do a:

  make flcards

the flcards binary will be available in fltk folder
